content:
Ion is iconic and very well managed. It has a great reception manned by friendly and well-mannered staff. Famous for its boutiques, jewellers, food and entertainment - it houses the world best names. Some of my favorite destinations at Ion Mall are;
The Imperial steamboat, Honeymoon desserts, Jasons, Taiwan fishball, popiah( at the Food court), Jeric hair salon, Toss & Turn, and also also its many little kiosks.
Ion is international and also has an underground transport access. A great stop for the family.
